Detailed Description

cvmx_npei_dma_pcie_req_num

NPEI_DMA_PCIE_REQ_NUM = NPEI DMA PCIE Outstanding Read Request Number

Outstanding PCIE read request number for DMAs and Packet, maximum number is 16
